{
  "stem": "26465.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because I wasn't even aware-- strange as it may be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was sort of-- I was probably in denial of it all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't know that they were being burnt-- that they were being cremated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were being probably used some kind of gas on them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and, of course, thousands of them went to the inferno there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It-- it hurt beyond human endurance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was-- at that time, there was no race-- no conception of whether you were French or Gypsy or Polish or Jewish.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was no-- everybody was in the same-- in the same-- hell-- that's what I'd call it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was hell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And all you could do is just stare ahead of you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were so dehumanized that, all through life, you never will regain your humanity.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You will never feel that you're somebody or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "A lot of people, even though they went out of the concentration camp-- they simply deteriorated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They either got very sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They got very, very negative in their lives, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they were-- most of them-- I don't know, but they suffered terrible depression-- bouts of depression.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You cannot get over it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I myself, I have been treated for depression for many, many years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Dachau till December-- December of '42.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then there was this group of men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They looked like businessmen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And our lagerfuherin-- the lager lady-- came, and she called some people that was her whim, I believe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she called aloud.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We lined up outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the men were just staring at us, like you would stare at a horse that you are going to buy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And touching our muscles, our hands, and-- and even asked to show our teeth to them, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
